# Copy to .env.local for local dev (vercel dev), and set the same value in your
# Vercel project's Environment Variables for production.

# The deployed Google Apps Script web app URL (ends in /exec).
# Get it from the Sheet: Extensions → Apps Script → Deploy → New deployment →
# Web app. See apps-script/Code.gs and README.md for the full walkthrough.
APPS_SCRIPT_URL=
